paragraphs.text:
%sql
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS AIRLINE_SIMULATION_LOC;
create table AIRLINE_SIMULATION_LOC
(
ID LONG NOT NULL,
Year INTEGER NOT NULL,
Month INTEGER NOT NULL,
DayofMonth INTEGER NOT NULL,
DayOfWeek INTEGER NOT NULL,
DepTime INTEGER,
CRSDepTime INTEGER,
ArrTime INTEGER,
CRSArrTime INTEGER,
UniqueCarrier VARCHAR(25),
FlightNum INTEGER,
TailNum VARCHAR(25),
ActualElapsedTime INTEGER,
CRSElapsedTime INTEGER,
AirTime INTEGER,
ArrDelay INTEGER,
DepDelay INTEGER,
Origin VARCHAR(25),
Dest VARCHAR(25),
Distance INTEGER,
TaxiIn INTEGER,
TaxiOut INTEGER,
Cancelled INTEGER,
CancellationCode VARCHAR(25),
Diverted INTEGER,
CarrierDelay INTEGER,
WeatherDelay INTEGER,
NASDelay INTEGER,
SecurityDelay INTEGER,
LateAircraftDelay INTEGER,
DestLon DOUBLE,
DestLat DOUBLE,
OrigLon DOUBLE,
OrigLat DOUBLE
)
USING COLUMN OPTIONS (PARTITION_BY 'UNIQUECARRIER')
as (select AIRLINE_SIMULATION.*, destlatitude, destnlongitude, originlatitude, originlongitude from AIRLINE_SIMULATION left outer join AIRLINE_DESTINATION_LOOKUP on AIRLINE_SIMULATION.DEST = AIRLINE_DESTINATION_LOOKUP.DESTIATA LEFT OUTER JOIN AIRLINE_ORIGIN_LOOKUP on AIRLINE_SIMULATION.ORIGIN = AIRLINE_ORIGIN_LOOKUP.ORIGINIATA ORDER BY ID);
